            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Should you buy followers to increase growth rate?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Purchased followers don't engage, which crushes your engagement rate and signals to the algorithm to downrank your content. Organic growth from real audience is the only kind worth measuring.</p></div></div>
